words.hint: Looks sweet, tastes like a factory mistake

When you realize you just blinked through an entire day
The sound of civilization collapsing gracefully
So confident it loops back to questionable
You don’t have style, you *radiate* it (allegedly)
A silly little guy, fighting for his life emotionally
When your friend steals a fry like it’s law
Caused by TikTok exposure over recommended dose
Not bad, not good, just aggressively existing
That 4 a.m. stare into the fridge type beat
Social media combat, bloodless but brutal
